                     <interp inst="t17890909-124-person1092" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw Mr. Burford run and seize this prisoner Davis; I assisted him; that is the same man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17890909-124-person1093">
                  ANN
                   HINDES
               <interp inst="t17890909-124-person1093" type="surname" value="HINDES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890909-124-person1093" type="given" value="ANN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890909-124-person1093" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I was looking out at my three pair of stairs window, on the 27th of August last, between four and five; and I saw the two prisoners taking the linen off the line, out of Mr. Bird's house, the one pair of stairs room; I live opposite; I never saw either of them before to my remembrance; the line where the clothes hung was close to the window; the windows were open; I am quite sure the prisoners are the men, because I hastened down to give the alarm; and I saw the prisoners come out at the door; one had a bundle; that was Williams; the gentleman that stands next to me.</p>
               <p>
            
