               <p>Court to Smith. Who picked up the bundle in the house? - A gentlewoman in the one pair of stairs; she is not here.</p>
               <p>Prisoner Davis. I leave it entirely to my counsel, Mr. Garrow.</p>
               <p>The prisoner Davis called four witnesses who all gave him a very good character.</p>
